      "line": 1,
      "description": "## The Components Folder\n\nThis is where all our **UI building blocks** live.\n\n### We organize components by size:\n\n```\ncomponents/\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ atoms/       ‚Üí Smallest pieces (Button, Icon, Input)\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ molecules/   ‚Üí Groups of atoms (SearchBar, ListingCard)\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ organisms/   ‚Üí Complex sections (Navbar, Footer)\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ layouts/     ‚Üí Page templates (MainLayout)\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ pages/       ‚Üí Full pages (Home, Search)\n```\n\n### Think of it like building with LEGO:\n- **Atoms** = Individual LEGO bricks\n- **Molecules** = Small structures (like a mini car)\n- **Organisms** = Bigger structures (like a house)\n- **Pages** = Complete creations\n\n**This pattern is called \"Atomic Design\" - we'll cover it in detail in Tour 03!**"
