      "description": "## Atoms Folder\n\nAtoms are the **smallest, simplest** components. They do one thing and do it well.\n\n### Our atoms:\n\n| Component | What it shows |\n|-----------|---------------|\n| **Avatar** | User's profile picture |\n| **Badge** | Small labels (like \"New\" or \"Popular\") |\n| **Button** | Clickable buttons |\n| **Icon** | Small symbols (like a heart or star) |\n| **Input** | Text boxes for typing |\n| **Price** | Money amounts (‚Çπ2,500) |\n| **Rating** | Star ratings (‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÜ) |\n| **Skeleton** | Loading placeholders |\n| **Tag** | Filter tags |\n\n### Each atom has its own folder with:\n- `Button.tsx` - The component code\n- `ButtonProps.ts` - Type definitions\n- `Button.stories.tsx` - Examples for Storybook\n- `index.ts` - Export file"
