      "line": 1,
      "description": "## Inside a Component Folder\n\nEvery component follows the **same structure**. This makes it easy to find things.\n\n### Example: Button component\n```\nButton/\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Button.tsx         ‚Üí The actual component\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ButtonProps.ts     ‚Üí What options (props) it accepts\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Button.stories.tsx ‚Üí Examples for documentation\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ index.ts           ‚Üí Makes importing easier\n```\n\n### What's in each file?\n\n**ButtonProps.ts** (this file):\n- Defines what options the button accepts\n- Example: size, color, text, onClick function\n\n**Button.tsx**:\n- The actual code that renders the button\n\n**Button.stories.tsx**:\n- Examples showing different button styles\n- Used in Storybook documentation"
