      "description": "## Layouts Folder\n\nLayouts are **page templates** that wrap around content.\n\n### What's a layout?\nImagine a picture frame - the frame stays the same, but the picture inside changes. Layouts work the same way!\n\n### MainLayout includes:\n- Navbar at the top (always visible)\n- Content area in the middle (changes per page)\n- Footer at the bottom (always visible)\n- Mobile navigation (on phones)\n\n### Our layouts:\n\n| Layout | Used for |\n|--------|----------|\n| **MainLayout** | Most pages (Home, Search, Details) |\n| **AuthLayout** | Login and Register pages |\n| **CheckoutLayout** | Booking and payment pages |\n| **DashboardLayout** | Provider/admin pages |\n\n### Why use layouts?\n- **Avoid repeating code** - Don't write the same navbar on every page\n- **Consistency** - All pages look similar\n- **Easy updates** - Change the navbar once, it updates everywhere"
