      "file": "src/components/atoms/Button/Button.tsx",
      "line": 1,
      "description": "## üìã To Do: Create Your First Component\n\nLet's practice by creating a new atom component: a `Tooltip` component.\n\n---\n\n### Step 1: Create the Folder Structure\n```bash\nmkdir -p src/components/atoms/Tooltip\n```\n\n### Step 2: Create the Props File\nCreate `src/components/atoms/Tooltip/TooltipProps.ts`:\n```typescript\nexport interface TooltipProps {\n  /** The text to show in the tooltip */\n  text: string;\n  /** Where to position the tooltip */\n  position?: 'top' | 'bottom' | 'left' | 'right';\n  /** The element that triggers the tooltip */\n  children: React.ReactNode;\n}\n```\n\n### Step 3: Create the Component\nCreate `src/components/atoms/Tooltip/Tooltip.tsx`:\n```typescript\nimport { TooltipProps } from './TooltipProps';\n\nexport function Tooltip({ \n  text, \n  position = 'top', \n  children \n}: TooltipProps) {\n  return (\n    <div className={`tooltip tooltip-${position}`} data-tip={text}>\n      {children}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n### Step 4: Create the Index File\nCreate `src/components/atoms/Tooltip/index.ts`:\n```typescript\nexport { Tooltip } from './Tooltip';\nexport type { TooltipProps } from './TooltipProps';\n```\n\n### Step 5: Export from Atoms Index\nAdd to `src/components/atoms/index.ts`:\n```typescript\nexport * from './Tooltip';\n```\n\n---\n\n## ‚ö†Ô∏è Watch Out For\n\n| Issue | Cause | Solution |\n|-------|-------|----------|\n| Component not found after import | Missing export | Check `index.ts` exports |\n| Props not autocompleting | Missing type export | Export both component AND props |\n| Styles not applying | Wrong class names | Check DaisyUI documentation |\n| File not saved | IDE sync issue | Save all files (Cmd+S or Ctrl+S) |\n\n---\n\n## ‚ùå Common Errors\n\n| Error Message | What It Means | How to Fix |\n|---------------|---------------|------------|\n| `Cannot find module './TooltipProps'` | File not created or wrong name | Check filename matches import |\n| `'Tooltip' is not exported` | Missing export statement | Add `export` keyword before function |\n| `Property 'X' is missing` | Required prop not provided | Pass all required props |\n| `Type 'X' is not assignable` | Wrong prop type | Check prop interface definition |\n\n---\n\n### ‚úÖ Checklist\n- [ ] Created folder: `src/components/atoms/Tooltip/`\n- [ ] Created `TooltipProps.ts` with interface\n- [ ] Created `Tooltip.tsx` with component\n- [ ] Created `index.ts` with exports\n- [ ] Added export to `src/components/atoms/index.ts`\n- [ ] Tested component in another file"
